Slip 1
1)	Create a container, add row inside it and add 3 columns inside row using Bootstrap.
Solution: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bootstrap Layout</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 bg-primary text-white p-3">
            Column 1
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 bg-success text-white p-3">
            Column 2
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 bg-danger text-white p-3">
            Column 3
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>



Slip 2
1.	Write the HTML5 code for generating the form as shown below. Apply the internal CSS to the following form to change the font size of the heading to 6pt and change the color to red and also change the background color to yellow.
Solution: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Project Management Form</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #e0f7fa;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 6pt;  /* As required */
        color: red;      /* As required */
        text-align: center;
    }
    .form-box {
        width: 350px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: yellow; /* Required background color */
        border-radius: 10px;
    }
    input, textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 8px;
        margin: 8px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border: 1px solid #aaa;
    }
    .priority-group {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
    button {
        padding: 8px 18px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-right: 10px;
        color: white;
    }
    .submit-btn {
        background: green;
    }
    .clear-btn {
        background: blue;
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<h2>Project Management</h2>
<div class="form-box">
    <form>
        <label>Project Name</label>
        <input type="text" placeholder="project name">
        <label>Assigned To</label>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Name">
        <label>Start Date</label>
        <input type="date">
        <label>End Date</label>
        <input type="date">
        <label>Priority</label>
        <div class="priority-group">
            <input type="radio" name="p"> High
            <input type="radio" name="p"> Average
            <input type="radio" name="p"> Low
        </div>
        <label>Description</label>
        <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Enter description"></textarea>
        <button class="submit-btn">Submit</button>
        <button type="reset" class="clear-btn">Clear</button>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>
