Solution: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Student Registration Form</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>College Admission – Student Registration Form</h2>
<form>
    <label>Full Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" required><br><br>
    <label>Email ID:</label><br>
    <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required><br><br>
    <label>Search Course:</label><br>
    <input type="search" placeholder="Search course"><br><br>
    <label>Date of Birth:</label><br>
    <input type="date" required><br><br>
    <label>Contact Number:</label><br>
    <input type="tel" placeholder="9876543210" required><br><br>
    <label>Gender:</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="gender"> Male
    <input type="radio" name="gender"> Female
    <input type="radio" name="gender"> Other<br><br>
    <label>Select Course:</label><br>
    <select>
        <option>B.Sc</option>
        <option>B.Com</option>
        <option>BCA</option>
        <option>BA</option>
        <option>M.Sc</option>
    </select><br><br>
    <label>Address:</label><br>
    <textarea rows="3" cols="30"></textarea><br><br>
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    <button type="reset">Reset</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>

Slip 7
1.	Create a web page that shows use of transition properties, transition delay and duration effect.
Solution: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>CSS Transition Example</title>
<style>
    .box {
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
        background: orange;
        margin: 50px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        /* Transition Effects */
        transition-property: width, height, background-color;
        transition-duration: 2s;     /* animation time */
        transition-delay: 0.5s;      /* wait before starting */
    }
    .box:hover {
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
        background: rgb(0, 140, 255);
    }
    h2 {
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>CSS Transition, Delay & Duration Demo</h2>
<div class="box"></div>
</body>
</html>

