Slip 10
1.	Design an appropriate HTML form for customer registration visiting a departmental store. Form should consist of fields such as name, contact no, gender, preferred days of purchasing, favorite item (to be selected from a list of items), suggestions etc. You should provide a button to submit as well as reset the form contents.
Solution: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Customer Registration Form</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body{
            font-family: Arial;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        form{
            width: 380px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        input, select, textarea{
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            border: 1px solid #777;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        label{font-weight: bold;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Customer Registration Form</h2>
<form>
    <label>Full Name:</label>
    <input type="text" required placeholder="Enter your name">
    <label>Contact Number:</label>
    <input type="tel" required placeholder="Mobile number">
    <label>Gender:</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="g" value="Male"> Male
    <input type="radio" name="g" value="Female"> Female
    <input type="radio" name="g" value="Other"> Other
    <br><br>
    <label>Preferred Days of Purchasing:</label><br>
    <input type="checkbox" value="Monday"> Monday
    <input type="checkbox" value="Friday"> Friday
    <input type="checkbox" value="Sunday"> Sunday
    <br><br>
    <label>Favorite Item:</label>
    <select>
        <option>Select an Item</option>
        <option>Groceries</option>
        <option>Clothes</option>
        <option>Electronics</option>
        <option>Cosmetics</option>
        <option>Furniture</option>
    </select>
    <label>Suggestions:</label>
    <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Enter your suggestions..."></textarea>
    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    <input type="reset" value="Reset">
</form>
</body>
</html>

