Slip 12
1.	Design an HTML form to take the information of a customer for booking a travel plan consisting of fields such as name, address, contact no., gender, preferred season(Checkboxes), location type(to be selected from a list) etc. You should provide button to submit as well as reset the form contents.
Solution: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Travel Booking Form</title>
</head>

<body>

<h2>Travel Plan Booking Form</h2>

<form>

    <label><b>Name:</b></label><br>
    <input type="text" name="name" required><br><br>

    <label><b>Address:</b></label><br>
    <textarea name="address" rows="3" cols="30" required></textarea><br><br>
    <label><b>Contact Number:</b></label><br>
    <input type="tel" name="contact" required><br><br>
    <label><b>Gender:</b></label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="g" value="Male"> Male
    <input type="radio" name="g" value="Female"> Female
    <input type="radio" name="g" value="Other"> Other
    <br><br>
    <label><b>Preferred Season:</b></label><br>
    <input type="checkbox" value="Winter"> Winter
    <input type="checkbox" value="Summer"> Summer
    <input type="checkbox" value="Rainy"> Rainy
    <br><br>
    <label><b>Location Type:</b></label><br>
    <select name="location">
        <option>Select a Type</option>
        <option>Hill Station</option>
        <option>Beach</option>
        <option>Desert</option>
        <option>City Tour</option>
        <option>Wildlife Safari</option>
    </select>
    <br><br>

    <label><b>Extra Suggestions:</b></label><br>
    <textarea name="suggestions" rows="3" cols="30"></textarea><br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    <input type="reset" value="Reset">
</form>
</body>
</html>

